= SDL_GetModState =
Use this function to get the current key modifier state for the keyboard.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_Keymod SDL_GetModState(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns an OR'd combination of the modifier keys for the keyboard. See [[SDL_Keymod]] for details.

